reviewText: Kids really enjoy the shows. No problems, shipped and delivered on time.
Arrived very quickly. This is a must get for angry bird lovers
My 8 year old loves this. Watches over and over again. Quick delivery with no problems.
Grandson liked it...that's all that matters.
this is another one of my grandson favorites.  he takes turns with this one and the transformers.  sometimes he can't pick with one he wants to watch first.

This volume of Season Two is great. I am a big Angry Birds fan.
The special features in this DVD are great. I am so happy that I added that to my 'Angry Birds Toons' DVD collection.
